%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20storied%20chocolate%20maker%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20lost%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F875-brands-reapply-put-royal-coat-of-arms-on-products-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroyal%20warrant%20from%20the%20British%20monarchy%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20170%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20warrant%2C%20which%20symbolizes%20that%20a%20company%20supplies%20goods%20or%20services%20to%20the%20royal%20family%2C%20was%20initially%20awarded%20by%20Queen%20Victoria%20in%201854.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Cadbury%20was%20absent%20from%20the%20list%20that%20was%20updated%20by%20The%20Royal%20Warrant%20Holders%20Association%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20had%20held%20its%20warrant%20uninterrupted%20for%20170%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fnews%2F2024%2F12%2F22%2Fcadburys-loses-royal-warrant-170-years-chocolate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20Telegraph.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fall-differences-cadbury-chocolate-india-the-uk-food-wars-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echocolate%20maker%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20a%20long%20history%20and%20huge%20popularity%20in%20the%20UK.%20According%20to%20trade%20publication%20The%20Grocer%2C%20its%20Dairy%20Milk%20was%20the%20most%20popular%20chocolate%20brand%20in%20the%20UK%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMailOnline%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-14217655%2FKing-strips-Cadbury-Royal-Warrant-Queens-favourite-chocolate.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20companies%20that%20didn't%20have%20their%20warrants%20renewed%20were%20notified%20by%20letters%2C%20but%20that%2C%20per%20protocol%2C%20the%20letters%20didn't%20give%20a%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECadbury%20was%20bought%20by%20US%20conglomerate%20Kraft%20in%202010%2C%20with%20K