20altogether%20in%20favor%20of%20handwritten%20letters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20you're%20looking%20to%20mix%20up%20your%20Santa's%20snacks%20or%20just%20learn%20something%20new%20this%20holiday%20season%2C%20here's%20a%20peek%20at%20how%20Christmas%20is%20celebrated%20around%20the%20world%20through%2012%20treats%20families%20leave%20for%20the%20man%20with%20the%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EUnited%20States%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225110%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20plate%20of%20cookies%20and%20a%20glass%20of%20milk%20in%20the%20foreground%20with%20a%20lit%20Christmas%20tree%20and%20fireplace%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67571ecf4adc4cc134355a22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223824%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChildren%20in%20the%20US%20leave%20milk%20and%20cookies%20for%20Santa.%3Cp%3Erangizzz%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20many%20children%20leave%20out%20a%20glass%20of%20milk%20and%20a%20plate%20of%20cookies%20for%20Santa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20families%20also%20leave%20carrots%20and%20celery%20for%20Santa's%20reindeer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAustralia%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225141%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20Santa%20Claus%20holding%20a%20a%20tall%20pint%20glass%20of%20light%20beer.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6757169a4adc4cc134355509%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223856%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20Australia%2C%20children%20leave%20Santa%20beer.%3Cp%3EReshetnikov_art%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Australians%20leave%20cookies%20for%20Santa%20to%20snack%20on%2C%20they%20replace%20the%20glass%20of%20milk%20with%20a%20cold%20glass%20of%20beer.%20December%20is%20actually%20summer%20for%20Australia%2C%20so%20the%20beer%20might%20be%20just%20what%20Santa%20needs%20in%20the%20hot%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E