ass%20matches%20picking%20101%20wickets.%20In%2020%20List%20A%20matches%20he%20has%2020%20scalps%20while%20in%2033%20T20%20games%20he%20has%2033%20wickets.%20The%20player%20previously%20toured%20Australia%20with%20the%20India%20A%20team%20ahead%20of%20the%20Border%20Gavaskar%20Trophy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKotian%20has%20been%20added%20as%20a%20safety%20net%20and%20also%20to%20keep%20the%20squad%20number%20intact%20for%20the%20last%20two%20games.%20He%20only%20comes%20into%20the%20picture%20if%20either%20among%20Washy%20or%20Jaddu%20(Ravindra%20Jadeja)%20gets%20injured%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20BCCI%20source%20told%20PTI%20on%20conditions%20of%20anonymity.%20%C2%A0The%20bowling%20all-rounder%20picked%20two%20wickets%20and%20scored%20an%20unbeaten%2039%20for%20Mumbai%20in%20their%20Vijay%20Hazare%20Trophy%20match%20against%20Hyderabad%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKotian%20has%20fond%20memories%20of%20the%20Melbourne%20Cricket%20Ground%20where%20he%20scored%2044%20batting%20at%20No.%208%20for%20India%20A%20and%20looked%20the%20part.%20He%20already%20has%20101%20wickets%20to%20his%20name%20and%201525%20runs%20with%20two%20centuries%20in%2033%20first-class%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%2C%20Axar%20Patel%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20summoned%20to%20Australia%20but%20as%20per%20sources%2C%20the%20left%20arm%20spinner%20had%20sought%20a%20break%20after%20first%20two%20matches%20of%20Vijay%20Hazare%20Trophy%20due%20to%20a%20family%20commitment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKotian%20has%20been%20added%20to%20the%20squad%20following%20Ashwin's%20surprise%20retirement%20from%20international%20cricket%20following%20the%20draw%20Test%20in%20Brisbane.%20The%2038-year-old%20ended%20his%20glorious%20career%20as%20the%20second%20highest%20wicket%20taker%20for%20India%20behind%20Anil%20Kumble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20on%20Friday%20posted%20a%20heartwarming%20tribute%20video%20for%20recently%20retired%20spinner%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%2C%20who%20reflected%20on%20a%20very%20big%20promise%20he%20made%20to%20himself%20early%20in%20his%20career%20when%20Indian%20team%20registered%20a%20series%20loss%20against%20England%20at%20home.%20Ashwin%2C%20who%20announced%20his%20retirement%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Brisbane%20Test%20against%20Australia%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20was%20a%20crucial%20architect%20of%20India's%20home%20domination%20that%20lasted%20for%20over%2012%20years%20and%20kickstarted%20after%20India's%20loss%20to%20England%20in%20a%20Test%20series%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20lost%20the%20series%20at%20home%20to%20England%20in%202012%20by%201-2%20and%20Ashwin%20was%20early%20in%20his%20international%20career%20during%20that%20series.%20Ashwin%20did%20end%20up%20as%20India's%20second-highest%20wicket-taker%20in%20that%20series%20with%2014%20scalps%20and%20overall%20at%20fourth%20spot%2C%20but%20his%20bowling%20average%20of%2052.64%20and%20no%20four%20or%20five-wicket%20hauls%20meant%20he%20was%20out-bowled%20by%20England%20pair%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Monty%20Panesar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F755-monty-panesar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMonty%20Panesar%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Graeme%20Swann%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F406-graeme-swann-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGraeme%20Swann%3C%2Fa%3E%20(17%20and%2020%20wickets%20respectively)%20and%20compatriot%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pragyan%20Ojha%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F969-pragyan-ojha-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPragyan%20Ojha%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20topped%20the%20charts%20with%2020%20scalps%20at%20an%20average%20of%20around%2030%20and%20two%20five-wicket%20hauls%20and%20best%20figures%20of%205%2F45.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%2C%20then%20a%20youngster%2C%20was%20dejected%20by%20this%20series%20loss%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20a%20setback%20at%20familiar%20home%2