B928%2C000%20crore%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%94an%20amount%20that%20is%20close%20to%2070%25%20of%20all%20the%20investment%20the%20state%20received%20in%20five%20years%20beginning%202017.%20For%20a%20change%2C%20promises%20have%20been%20followed%20by%20concrete%20actions%20on%20the%20ground.%20The%20group%20has%20already%20begun%20its%20investments%2C%20focusing%20on%20three%20key%20sectors%3A%20logistics%2C%20gas%20distribution%2C%20and%20agri-logistics.%20These%20initiatives%20have%20already%20generated%20over%2025%2C000%20direct%20and%20indirect%20jobs.%20Further%20investments%20in%20these%20sectors%20are%20expected%20to%20create%20an%20additional%2027%2C000%20job%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20boost%20from%20a%20big%20investor%20like%20the%20Adani%20Group%20is%20exactly%20what%20Bihar%20had%20been%20waiting%20for.%20It%20couldn't%20have%20come%20at%20a%20more%20opportune%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20rewind%20a%20bit%20to%20understand%20why%20Bihar%20desperately%20needed%20this%20push%20now.%20In%20the%201980s%2C%20the%20agricultural%20sector%20accounted%20for%20nearly%2051%25%20of%20Bihar's%20economy%2C%20significantly%20higher%20than%20the%20national%20average%20of%2036%25.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20industrial%20sector%20contributed%20a%20meagre%2010%25%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20national%20average%20of%2025%25.%20While%20these%20two%20sectors%20prospered%20in%20most%20parts%20of%20India%20during%20the%201990s%2C%20Bihar%20experienced%20a%20painful%20and%20accelerated%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20period%20also%20coincided%20with%20a%20population%20explosion%20in%20the%20state.%20As%20opportunities%20dwindled%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20education%2C%20healthcare%2C%20jobs%2C%20housing%2C%20value-added%20food%20items%2C%20and%20vehicles%20sharply%20increased.%20With%20investment%20rates%20crawling%20in%20the%20low%20single%20digits%20and%20capacity%20addition%20at%20dismal%20levels%2C%20Biharis%20were%20left%20with%20little%20choice%20but%20to%20migrate.%20The%20scale%20of%20this%20migration%2C%20however%2C%20took%20everyone%20by%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20study%2C%20%E2%80%9CAbout%2055%25%20of%20households%20have%20at%20least%20one%20migrant%20worker.%20More%20than%2090%25%20of%20migrant%20workers%20work%20outside%20Bihar%2C%20with%20a%20little%20over%2085%25%20employed%20in%20urban%20areas%20outside%20the%20state%2C%20particularly%20in%20construction%20and%20manufacturing%20sectors.%20By%20far%2C%20the%20dominant%20form%20of%20migrant%20work%20is%20in%20urban%20centres%20in%20other%20states%2C%20making%20it%20relatively%20long-distance%20in%20nature.%20Nearly%20all%20migrant%20workers%20from%20rural%20Bihar%20are%20male%2C%20and%20three-quarters%20of%20them%20are%20below%2045%20years%20of%20age.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20migration%20narrative%20persisted%2C%20the%20pandemic%20struck%2C%20severely%20impacting%20lives%20and%20livelihoods.%20It%20dealt%20a%20significant%20blow%20to%20the%20very%20idea%20of%20migration%2C%20and%20Bihar%20has%20yet%20to%20fully%20recover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20called%20for%20a%20reimagining%20of%20Bihar.%20The%20idea%20of%20holding%20an%20investment%20summit%2C%20the%20first%20edition%20of%20which%20took%20place%20in%202023%2C%20could%20not%20have%20come%20at%20a%20more%20opportune%20moment.%20During%20the%20inaugural%20summit%2C%20MOUs%20worth%20%E2%82%B950%2C000%20crore%20were%20signed%2C%20and%20the%20figure%20skyrocketed%20to%20%E2%82%B91.8%20lakh%20crore%20in%20the%20second%20edition%20this%20year.%20A%20big%20share%20of%20that%20came%20from%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20which%20emerged%20as%20the%20largest%20investor%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EViksit%20Bharat%20Can't%20Be%20Without%20Bihar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20years%20of%20growth%20fuelled%20by%20a%20very%20low%20base%20and%20remittance-driven%20services%20sector%2C%20Bihar%20continues%20to%20rank%20near%20the%20bottom%20on%20almost%20all%20development%20parameters.%20Its%20per%20capita%20income%20is%20just%2033%25%20of%20India's%20average%2C%20a%20significant%20decline%20from%2070%25%20in%20the%201960s.%20The%20state's%20level%20of%20urbanization%20is%20alarmingly%20low%20at%2012%25%2C%20far%20below%20the%20national%20average%20of%20nearly%2035%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Bihar%20is%20home%20to%20nearly%209%25%20of%20India's%20population%2C%20its%20contribution%20to%20the%20country's%20GDP%20is%20only%202.8%25%20today.%20In%201961%2C%20it%20contributed%207.8%25%2C%20slightly%20less%20than%20Maharashtra%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal.%20While%20most%20other%20states%20have%20maintained%20or%20increased%20their%20share%E2%80%94states%20like%20Karnataka%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Gujarat%20have%20seen%20significant%20rises%E2%80%94Bihar%20has%20experienced%20a%20steep%20decline%20over%20the%20past%20six%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20by%20the%20PM's%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20observes%20that%20%E2%80%9Cafter%20a%20decade%20of%20modest%20improvement%20from%2031.2%25%20for%20bifurcated%20Bihar%20in%202000-01%20to%20reach%2035.4%25%20by%202010-11%2C%20its%20relative%20per%20capita%20now%20hovers%20around%2033%25.%20Though%20this%20means%20that%20an%20average%20person%20in%20Bihar%20still%20has%20an%20income%20level%2077%25%20lower%20than%20that%20of%20an%20average%20Indian.%20We%20understand%20that%20household%20incomes%20may%20be%20bolstered%20by%20remittances%20but%20the%20gap%20is%20very%20stark%E2%80%A6.Bihar%20will%20need%20to%20accelerate%20its%20economic%20growth%20considerably%20to%20make%20progress%20toward%20closing%20this%20gap.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20massive%20investment%20from%20the%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%94as%20well%20as%20from%20other%20companies%20such%20as%20NTPC%20Green%2C%20Ashoka%20Buildcon%2C%20Shree%20Cements%2C%20NHPC%2C%20Coca-Cola%2C%20and%20Haldiram%E2%80%94can%20help%20the%20state%20make%20a%20quantum%20leap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20needs%20a%20paradigm%20shift%2C%20and%20investment-led%20growth%20is%20the%20only%20option%20it%20has%20at%20the%20moment.%20The%20political%20class%20must%20do%20everything%20possible%20to%20ensure%20the%20state%20remains%20investor-friendly.%20After%20all%2C%20migrants%20like%20me%20and%20many%20others%20deserve%20the%20option%20to%20return%20to%20our%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20Consulting%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734955800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fcnaf2hu8_bihar-generic_625x300_20_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffinally-the-headline-bihar-has-been-waiting-for-7314913%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20massive%20investment%20from%20the%20Adani%20Groupas%20well%20as%20from%20other%20companies%20such%20as%20NTPC%20Green%2C%20Ashoka%20Buildcon%2C%20Shree%20Cements%2C%20NHPC%2C%20Coca-Cola%2C%20and%20Haldiramcan%20help%20the%20state%20make%20a%20quantum%20leap.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffinally-the-headline-bihar-has-been-waiting-for-7314913%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Luigi%20Mangione%20faces%20terror%20charges%20in%20UnitedHealth%20CEO%20murder%20case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734955787000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116600893%2Cimgsize-48704.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fluigi-mangione-faces-terror-charges-in-unitedhealth-ceo-brian-thompson-murder-case%2Farticleshow%2F116600890.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Luigi%20Mangione%20will%20be%20arraigned%20Monday%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20UnitedHealth%20G