y'%20For%20Classes%205%20And%208%20Students%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20big%20change%20in%20school%20education%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20scrapped%20the%20'no-detention%20policy'%20for%20classes%205%20and%208%20in%20schools%20governed%20by%20it%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20fail%20students%20who%20do%20not%20clear%20the%20year-end%20exams%2C%20according%20to%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2016%20states%20and%20two%20Union%20Territories%20have%20already%20done%20away%20with%20the%20'no-detention%20policy'%20for%20the%20two%20grades%20after%20an%20amendment%20to%20the%20Right%20to%20Education%20Act%20(RTE)%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20official%20notification%2C%20if%20students%20fail%20to%20clear%20the%20annual%20exams%2C%20they%20will%20be%20given%20additional%20coaching%20and%20an%20opportunity%20to%20take%20a%20re-exam%20within%20two%20months%20of%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20child%20appearing%20in%20the%20re-examination%20fails%20to%20fulfil%20the%20promotion%20criteria%20again%2C%20he%20shall%20be%20held%20back%20in%20fifth%20class%20or%20eighth%20class%2C%20as%20the%20case%20may%20be.%20During%20the%20holding%20back%20of%20the%20child%2C%20the%20class%20teacher%20shall%20guide%20the%20child%20as%20well%20as%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20child%2C%20if%20necessary%2C%20and%20provide%20specialised%20inputs%20after%20identifying%20the%20learning%20gaps%20at%20various%20stages%20of%20assessment%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notification%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20no%20child%20can%20be%20expelled%20by%20any%20school%20until%20their%20education%20is%20complete%2C%20the%20government%20has%20clarified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20senior%20Education%20Ministry%20officials%2C%20the%20notification%20will%20apply%20to%20over%203%2C000%20schools%20run%20by%20the%20central%20government%2C%20including%20Kendriya%20Vidyalayas%2C%20Navaodyala%20Vidyalayas%20and%20Sainik%20Schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp