0have%20opted%20into%20text%20reminders%2C%26quot%3B%20McGovern%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20opt%20in%20to%20receive%20any%20kind%20of%20text%20message%20from%20a%20retailer.%20Keeping%20track%20of%20what%20you%20ordered%20and%20where%2C%20how%20it's%20being%20delivered%2C%20is%20really%20important.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScammers%20target%20the%20holiday%20season%20because%20it's%20a%20time%20when%20people%20are%20%26quot%3Bsuper%20busy%26quot%3B%20buying%20gifts%20for%20loved%20ones%2C%20McGovern%20said.%20It%20can%20be%20easy%20to%20fall%20for%20a%20phishing%20scam%20during%20this%20time%20of%20the%20year%2C%20McGovern%20said%2C%20because%20of%20the%20commotion%20around%20holiday%20shopping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20panicking%2C%20you%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20McGovern%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20a%20week%20from%20Christmas%2C%20and%20they're%20like%2C%20'Oh%20no%2C%20my%20package%20is%20being%20held%20up.%20It's%20something%20for%20my%20child.%20You're%20naturally%20going%20to%20go%20into%20panic%20mode.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20method%20to%20spot%20a%20phishing%20scam%20is%20to%20look%20at%20where%20the%20text%20or%20email%20is%20coming%20from%2C%20McGovern%20said.%20The%20USPS%20says%20it%20only%20uses%20%26quot%3B5-digit%20short%20codes%26quot%3B%20to%20send%20and%20receive%20text%20messages%20to%20and%20from%20mobile%20phones.%20One%20example%20of%20a%20fake%20scam%20text%20claiming%20to%20be%20from%20the%20USPS%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%20shows%20a%20%2B63%20area%20code%2C%20which%20originates%20in%20the%20Philippines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20phishing%2C%26quot%3B%20McGovern%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20got%20one%20the%20other%20day%20for%20my%20health%20insurance%2C%20and%20it%20looked%20like%20it%20was%20coming%20from%20your%20health%20insurance%2C%20until%20I%20looked%20at%20the%20address%20and%20realized%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20important%20thing%20to%20do%20if%20you%20think%20you%20are%20being%20scammed%20is%20to%20stop%2C%20pause%2C%20and%20look%20for%20warning%20signs%2C%20McGovern%20said.%20If%20you%20feel%20like%20something%20is%20off%2C%20there's%20a%20chance%20that%20it%20probably%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaw%20enforcement%20agencies%20have%20also%20reported%20a%20rise%20in%20%26quot%3Bporch%20pirate%26quot%3B%20activity%2C%20where%20thieves%20will%20steal%20a%20package%20delivered%20to%20someone's%20front%20porch.%20North%20Carolina%20Attorney%20General%20John%20Stein%20said%20in%20a%20holiday%20scam%20warning%20that%20it's%20important%20to%20track%20packages%20and%20make%20sure%20that%20you%20are%20home%20when%20they%20are%20delivered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20set%20the%20delivery%20address%20to%20a%20neighbor's%20house%20who%20is%20home%20during%20the%20day%2C%20send%20the%20package%20to%20your%20workplace%2C%20or%20ask%20the%20post%20office%20to%20hold%20your%20mail%20and%20collect%20the%20deliveries%20there%2C%20Stein%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fholiday-scams-learn-how-to-spot-and-avoid-them-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734951901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675f359f27808b3289cd46eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fholiday-scams-learn-how-to-spot-and-avoid-them-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Here%20are%20essential%20tips%20to%20safeguard%20your%20personal%20information%20and%20avoid%20fraud.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kniemeyer%40insider.com%20(Kenneth%20Niemeyer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fholiday-scams-learn-how-to-spot-and-avoid-them-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Today's%20Mortgage%20Rates%20%7C%20Inflation%20Needs%20to%20Slow%20Further%20for%20Rates%20to%20Drop%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETh