nt%20in%20Bangladesh%20has%20sent%20a%20diplomatic%20note%20and%20urged%20India%20to%20send%20deposed%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20back%20to%20Dhaka.%C2%A0The%2077-year-old%20Awami%20League%20leader%20has%20been%20living%20in%20India%20since%20August%205%20when%20she%20fled%20Bangladesh%20amid%20massive%20protests%20that%20brought%20down%20her%2016-year-old%20regime%20and%20forced%20her%20to%20flee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dhaka-based%20International%20Crimes%20Tribunal%20(ICT)%20has%20issued%20arrest%20warrants%20in%20names%20of%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20and%20her%20ministers%2C%20advisors%20and%20former%20military%20and%20civil%20officials%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20%26quot%3Bcrimes%20against%20humanity%20and%20genocide%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETouhid%20Hossain%2C%20the%20foreign%20affairs%20adviser%20in%20the%20interim%20government%2C%20told%20reporters%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20sent%20a%20note%20verbale%20(diplomatic%20message)%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%20saying%20that%20Bangladesh%20wants%20her%20back%20here%20for%20the%20judicial%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Home%20Advisor%20Jahangir%20Alam%20said%20his%20office%20has%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Ministry%20here%20to%20facilitate%20Ms%20Hasina's%20extradition.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20regarding%20her%20extradition.%20The%20process%20is%20currently%20underway%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Alam%20said%20an%20extradition%20treaty%20exists%20between%20Dhaka%20and%20New%20Delhi%20Ms%20Hasina%20could%20be%20taken%20back%20to%20Bangladesh%20under%20that%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20diplomatic%20communication%20seeking%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20return%20comes%20weeks%20after%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Vikram%20Misri%20visited%20Bangladesh%20and%20spoke%20to%20Chief%20Advisor%20in%20the%20interim%20government%2C%20Nobel%20laureate%20Muhammad%20Yunus.%20Speaking%20to%20reporters%20in%20Dhaka%2C%20Mr%20Misri%20had%20said%20he%20had%20a%20frank%2C%20candid%2C%20and%20constructive%20exchange%20of%20views%20with%20his%20interlocutors%20and%20discussed%20the%20entire%20gamut%20of%20issues%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20important%20bilateral%20relationship%26quot%3B.%20He%20said%20India%20had%20also%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20attacks%20on%20minorities%2C%20including%20Hindus%2C%20with%20Bangladesh%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20from%20the%20Chief%20Advisor's%20office%20had%20said%20that%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20stay%20in%20India%20was%20also%20discussed.%20The%20Chief%20Advisor%20had%20then%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20people%20are%20concerned%20because%20she%20is%20making%20many%20statements%20from%20there.%20It%20creates%20tensions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Foreign%20Secretary's%20visit%2C%20Ms%20Hasina%20targeted%20the%20interim%20government%20and%20accused%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20of%20running%20a%20%26quot%3Bfascist%20regime%26quot%3B.%20In%20a%20virtual%20address%20to%20Awami%20League%20supporters%20in%20London%2C%20she%20alleged%20that%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bmastermind%26quot%3B%20behind%20the%20political%20turmoil%20that%20ended%20her%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20August%205%2C%20the%20attacks%20on%20minorities%2C%20places%20of%20worship%20of%20Hindus%2C%20Christians%20and%20Buddhists%20have%20been%20rampant.%20We%20condemn%20it.%20The%20Jamaat%20and%20terrorists%20are%20having%20a%20free%20run%20under%20the%20new%20regime%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%26quot%3BBangladesh%20is%20now%20under%20the%20grip%20of%20a%20fascist%20regime%20where%20people's%20democratic%20rights%20have%20been%20obliterated.%20Our%20government's%20achievements%20in%20poverty%20alleviation%20and%20infrastructure%20development%2C%20strengthening%20of%20democracy%20were%20being%20undone%20under%20Yunus's%20leadership%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publish