%20has%20risen%20and%20with%20subsidies%20gone%2C%20cost%20of%20living%20has%20increased.%20So%20has%20poverty.%20Milei%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8NLzc9kobDk%5C%22%3Eclaims%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20rise%20in%20unemployment%20and%20poverty%20levels%20is%20because%20it%20is%20correctly%20reported%20now%20unlike%20earlier%20when%2C%20he%20alleges%2C%20the%20real%20levels%20were%20hidden.%20He%20doesn't%20have%20much%20time.%20Argentinians%20should%20feel%20the%20economic%20pain%20easing%20before%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mackinac.org%2FOvertonWindow%5C%22%3EOverton%20Window%3C%2Fa%3E%20shuts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaptain%20America%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilei%20is%20at%20the%20vanguard%20of%20mould-breaking%20leaders%20now%20active%20on%20the%20world%20stage.%20The%20most%20powerful%20of%20them%20is%20unquestionably%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20whose%20sheer%20audacity%20trumps%20his%20predecessors'%20promises%20of%20hope.%20In%20an%20astonishing%20rebound%20of%20political%20fortune%2C%20Trump%2C%20whose%20career%20seemed%20to%20be%20over%20in%202020%20when%20he%20was%20ejected%20from%20office%20branded%20as%20an%20insurrectionist%2C%20trounced%20the%20lacklustre%20Democratic%20Party%20candidate%20Kamala%20Harris%20to%20reclaim%20the%20White%20House%20after%20a%20gap%20of%20four%20years.%20His%20comeback%20is%20so%20decisive%20that%20the%20hub%20of%20activity%20has%20already%20shifted%20from%20Washington%20to%20Florida%20as%20world%20leaders%20and%20business%20tycoons%20drop%20by%20to%20dine%20on%20fast%20food.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20business%20barons%20are%20already%20prostrating%20before%20king%20Trump%20at%20his%20Palm%20Beach%20resort-residence%20Mar-a-Lago%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20the%20enormous%20power%20he%20has%20accumulated%20by%20winning%20the%20election%20on%20hard%20positions%2C%20over-the-top%20plans%20and%20scattershot%20threats.%20SoftBank's%20Masayoshi%20Son%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F12%2F16%2Fsoftbank-ceo-to-announce-100-billion-investment-in-us-during-visit-with-trump.html%5C%22%3Epledged%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20invest%20%24100%20billion%20in%20the%20US%20over%20the%20next%20four%20years.%20Singapore's%20ultra-cautious%20sovereign%20fund%20GIC%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-12-10%2Fsingapore-s-cautious-wealth-fund-gic-takes-more-private-markets-risk%3Fcmpid%3Dsocialflow-facebook-business%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dbusiness%26utm_campaign%3Dsocialflow-organic%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%5C%22%3Eramping%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20US%20exposure.%20Congratulating%20Trump%20on%20his%20election%20win%2C%20even%20Indian%20billionaire%20Gautam%20Adani%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fgautam_adani%2Fstatus%2F1856679498311184665%5C%22%3Epromised%20to%20invest%3C%2Fa%3E%20%2410%20billion%20in%20that%20country's%20energy%20and%20infrastructure%20sectors.%20Like%20his%20friend%20and%20admirer%20Milei%2C%20Trump%20has%20vowed%20to%20take%20the%20axe%20to%20government%20spending%20and%20slam%20rivals%20with%20earth-shattering%20trade%20tariffs%20while%20letting%20American%20businesses%20have%20a%20free%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20promise%20to%20radically%20break%20away%20from%20America's%20long-practised%20foreign%20policy%20is%20already%20forcing%20adjustments%20all%20over%20the%20world.%20His%20solution%20is%20simple%3A%20others'%20problems%20are%20not%20America's%20unless%20it's%20good%20for%20business.%20A%20non-interventionist%20US%20can%20lower%20the%20temperature%20in%20many%20conflict-ridden%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENATO%20members%20in%20Europe%20are%20mulling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fc4942166-c61b-46ec-832f-1671aecf1b02%5C%22%3Eraising%3C%2Fa%3E%20targeted%20defence%20spending%20to%203%25%20of%20GDP%20from%20the%20currently%20mandated%202%25%20of%20GDP.%20Israel%2C%20until%20now%20averse%20to%20a%20truce%20with%20Hamas%2C%20is%20said%20to%20be%20ready%20to%20make%20a%20deal.%20Some%20reports%20say%20that%20even%20Saudi%20Arabia%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fseymourhersh.substack.com%2Fp%2Fthe-new-ceasefire-equation%5C%22%3Emight%20be%20involved%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20rebuilding%20Gaza%20in%20what%20has%20hints%20of%20a%20near-two-state%20solution.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joker%20in%20the%20Trump%20pack%2C%20however%2C%20is%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20the%20billionaire%20designated%20to%20head%20a%20department%20of%20efficiency%20whose%20job%20would%20be%20to%20reprise%20what%20Milei%E2%80%94a%20Musk%20fanboy%E2%80%94did%20in%20Argentina.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Phrygia%E2%80%A6er%2C%20Turkey%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20cusp%20of%20Asia%20and%20Europe%2C%20where%20ancient%20Phrygia%20once%20existed%2C%20Turkey's%20President%20Recep%20Tayyip%20Erdogan%20appears%20to%20have%20hacked%20a%20knotty%20problem%20in%20his%20backyard.%20In%20a%20mere%2011%20days%2C%20an%20Idlib-based%20rebel%20militia%20led%20by%20a%20former%20Islamic%20State%20and%20Al%20Qaeda%20commander%2C%20Ahmed%20al-Shaara%2C%20known%20earlier%20by%20his%20nom%20de%20guerre%2C%20Abu%20Mohammad%20al-Jolani%2C%20successfully%20evicted%20Bashar%20al-Assad%2C%20the%20dynastic%20occupant%20of%20Damascus%20for%2024%20years.%20Reports%20suggest%20that%20the%20Hay'at%20Tahrir%20al-Sham%20(HTS)%2C%20which%20is%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20by%20several%20countries%2C%20including%20the%20US%20and%20Turkey%2C%20has%20the%20tacit%20support%20of%20the%20latter.%20Acknowledging%20that%20Turkey%20is%20a%20major%20military%20force%2C%20Trump%2C%20who%20gets%20along%20with%20the%20Turkish%20President%20very%20well%2C%20has%20said%20that%20Erdogan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.eu%2Farticle%2Fdonald-trump-says-turkey-orchestrated-bashar-assad-overthrow-in-syria%2F%5C%22%3Eorchestrated%20it.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20manoeuvre%20has%20decisively%20changed%20the%20power%20equations%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20HTS's%20assault%E2%80%94when%20a%20non-interventionist%20is%20poised%20to%20become%20the%20US%20President%20and%20Israel%20has%20pummeled%20to%20near-submission%20Iran-backed%20Hamas%20and%20Hezbollah%E2%80%94has%20cut%20off%20Iran%20and%20Russia%2C%20which%20was%20a%20staunch%20ally%20of%20Assad%2C%20from%20the%20region.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Nagorno-Karabakh%20conflict%20earlier%2C%20Turkey%20had%20already%20tested%20Russia%20and%20found%20that%20it%20would%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcarnegieendowment.org%2Frussia-eurasia%2Fpolitika%2F2023%2F10%2Flong-standing-ties-between-armenia-and-russia-are-fraying-fast%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%3Eunwilling%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20divert%20attention%20from%20Ukraine.%20Turkey's%20training%20and%20weapons%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gmfus.org%2Fnews%2Fturkeys-overlooked-role-second-nagorno-karabakh-war%5C%22%3Ehelped%3C%2Fa%3E%20Azerbaijan%20decisively%20wrest%20the%20region%20from%20Armenia%20in%20September%202023%2C%20which%20was%20under%20Russia's%20security%20umbrella%2C%20in%20a%20one-day%20putsch.%20Turkey%20also%20supplies%20the%20highly%20effective%20Bayraktar%20drones%20(although%20they%20are%20said%20to%20be%20less%20in%20use%20now)%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20their%20maker%2C%20Baykar%2C%20was%20even%20reported%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Faerospace-defense%2Fturkeys-drone-maker-baykar-begins-build-plant-ukraine-2024-02-06%2F%5C%22%3Ebuilding%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20factory%20near%20Kyiv.%20Erdogan%20perhaps%20wagered%2C%20correctly%2C%20that%20Russia%20would%20not%20intervene%20in%20Syria.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20mean%20the%20region%20will%20calm%20down.%20Far%20from%20it.%20But%20the%20slim%20odds%20for%20peace%20and%20rebuilding%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20have%20gone%20up%20a%20notch%20and%20can%20potentially%20mean%20millions%20of%20refugees%20who%20fled%20to%20Turkey%20and%20its%20European%20neighbours%20could%20return.%20Erdogan%20had%20tried%20in%202010%20to%20create%20a%20free%20trade%20zone%20with%20Jordan%2C%20Syria%20and%20Lebanon.%20A%20deal%20was%20signed%20but%20the%20region%20plunged%20into%20conflict%20soon%20after.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20unconventional%20leaders%20have%20been%20good%20or%20bad%20for%20their%20countries%20is%20debatable%2C%20but%20they%20definitely%20change%20the%20course%20of%20history.%20Nations%20such%20as%20Pakistan%20and%20Bangladesh%2C%20which%20are%20caught%20in%20a%20downward%20spiral%2C%20also%20need%20leaders%20who%20think%20out%20of%20the%20box.%20Events%20in%20both%20countries%20show%20that%20like%20Argentina%2C%20the%20Overton%20Window%20for%20drastic%20measures%20is%20open%20but%20the%20opportunity%20will%20not%20last%20for%20long.%20Perhaps%20new%20leaders%20will%20emerge%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Dinesh%20Narayanan%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20journalist%20and%20author%20of%20'The%20RSS%20And%20The%20Making%20Of%20The%20Deep%20Nation'.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734949920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F265g1thg_2024_625x300_23_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmilei-trump-erdogan-the-three-radicals-of-2024-7314114%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Whether%20unconventional%20leaders%20have%20been%20good%20or%20bad%20for%20their%20countries%20is%20debatable%2C%20but%20they%20definitely%20change%20the%20course%20of%20history.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmilei-trump-erdogan-the-three-radicals-of-2024-7314114%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20overdrinking%20wat