0not%20decided%20on%20a%20business%20integration%20yet%2C%20but%20in%20order%20to%20find%20a%20direction%20for%20the%20possibility%20of%20business%20integration%20by%20the%20end%20of%20January%202025%2C%20we%20strive%20to%20be%20the%20one%20and%20only%20leading%20company%20that%20creates%20new%20mobility%20value%20through%20a%20chemical%20reaction%20that%20can%20only%20be%20driven%20through%20the%20synthesis%20of%20the%20two%20teams.%26quot%3B%5Cn%3Ch2%3EPotential%20Opportunities%20From%20The%20MOU%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20coming%20together%2C%20Nissan%20and%20Honda%20aim%20to%20take%20down%20the%20largest%20automaker%20and%20take%20the%20spot%20of%20a%20world-class%20mobility%20company.%20The%20duo%20is%20targeting%20to%20achieve%20a%20revenue%20exceeding%2030%20trillion%20yen%20and%20an%20operating%20profit%20of%20more%20than%203%20trillion%20yen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EExpected%20synergies%20from%20the%20new%20joint%20holding%20company%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStandardization%20of%20vehicle%20platforms%20to%20achieve%20profitability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20brand%20will%20standardize%20platforms%20across%20its%20line-up%20to%20achieve%20cost%20efficiencies%20and%20reduced%20R%26amp%3BD%20costs.%20The%20integration%20will%20further%20reinforce%20sales%20and%20operations%20volumes%20while%20maximizing%20profits.%20With%20the%20mutual%20amalgam%20of%20global%20offerings%2C%20Nissan%20and%20Honda%20will%20be%20able%20to%20meet%20larger%20customer%20demands%20across%20the%20globe%20with%20ICE%2C%20HEV%2C%20PHEV%2C%20and%20EV%20vehicles.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EIntegration%20of%20R%26amp%3BD%20functions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnWith%20the%20joint%20research%20agreement%20on%20fundamental%20technologies%20signed%20on%20August%201%2C%20the%20two%20companies%20have%20started%20joint%20research%20in%20fundamental%20technologies%20in%20the%20area%20of%20vehicle%20platforms%20for%20next-generation%20software-defined%20vehicles%20(SDVs)%2C%20which%20is%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20the%20field%20of%20intelligence.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EOptimizing%20manufacturing%20systems%20and%20facilities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20companies%20anticipate%20that%20optimizing%20their%20manufacturing%20plants%20and%20energy%20service%20facilities%2C%20combined%20with%20improved%20collaboration%20through%20the%20shared%20use%20of%20production%20lines%2C%20will%20result%20in%20a%20substantial%20improvement%20in%20capacity%20utilization%20leading%20to%20a%20decrease%20in%20fixed%20costs.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EReinforcing%20supply%20chain%20by%20integration%20purchasing%20function%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnTo%20fully%20leverage%20the%20synergies%20from%20optimizing%20development%20and%20production%20capacity%2C%20both%20companies%20intend%20to%20boost%20their%20competitiveness%20by%20improving%20and%20streamlining%20purchasing%20operations%20and%20sourcing%20common%20parts%20from%20the%20same%20supply%20chain%20and%20in%20collaboration%20with%20business%20partners.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3ERealizing%20cost%20synergies%20through%20operational%20efficiency%20improvements%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20companies%20expect%20the%20integration%20of%20systems%2C%20back-office%20operations%2C%20sales%20channels%2C%20and%20talent%20pool%2C%20along%20with%20the%20upgrade%20and%20standardization%20of%20operational%20processes%20to%20drive%20cost%20reductions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EProcess%20Of%20Business%20Integration%20%26amp%3B%20Stock%20Transfer%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENissan%20and%20Honda%20have%20announced%20their%20plan%20to%20set%20up%20through%20a%20joint%20share%20transfer%2C%20a%20joint%20holding%20company%20that%20will%20be%20the%20parent%20company%20of%20both%20companies.%20This%20will%20be%20subject%20to%20approval%20at%20each%20company's%20general%20meeting%20of%20shareholders%20and%20obtaining%20necessary%20approvals%20from%20relevant%20authorities%20for%20this%20business%20integration%2C%20based%20on%20the%20premise%20that%20Nissan's%20turnaround%20actions%20are%20steadily%20executed.%20Both%20Nissan%20and%20Honda%20will%20be%20fully%20owned%20subsidiaries%20of%20the%20joint%20holding%20company.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20companies%20plan%20to%20continue%20coexisting%20and%20developing%20the%20brands%20held%20by%20Honda%20and%20Nissan%20equally.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3ESchedule%20of%20business%20transfer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%20border%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20cellpadding%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20data-sheets-baot%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20cellspacing%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20data-sheets-root%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ccolgroup%3E%5Cn%3Ccol%20width%3D%5C%22365%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ccol%20width%3D%5C%22145%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fcolgroup%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EEvent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EDate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EExecution%20of%20agreement%20concerning%20the%20business%20integration%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EJune%202025%20(planned)%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EExtraordinary%20shareholders'%20meeting%20of%20the%20companies%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EApril%202026%20(planned)%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EDelisting%20from%20the%20TSE%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EAugust%202026%20(planned)%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EEffective%20date%20of%20the%20share%20transfer%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EAugust%202026%20(planned)%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftbody%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftable%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EShare%20transfer%20ratio%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20share%20transfer%20ratio%20for%20the%20share%20transfer%20will%20be%20determined%20by%20the%20time%20of%20concluding%20the%20final%20definitive%20agreement%20regarding%20the%20business%20integration.%20The%20determination%20will%20be%20based%20on%20the%20results%20of%20due%20diligence%2C%20and%20third-party%20valu