1%20lakh%20subscribers%20on%20YouTube%2C%20her%20previous%20videos%20included%20tutorials%20on%20machine%20learning%20and%20neural%20networks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Dar%2C%20while%20considering%20a%20future%20in%20academia%2C%20ultimately%20decided%20to%20leave%20her%20PhD%20program.%20She%20weighed%20the%20potential%20benefits%20of%20a%20polished%20career%20in%20academia%20with%20the%20alternative%20path%20of%20becoming%20a%20professor%20and%20mentoring%20students.%20However%2C%20the%20tradeoffs%20associated%20with%20this%20lifestyle%20ultimately%20influenced%20her%20decision%20to%20pursue%20a%20different%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20whose%20lifestyles%20I%20thought%20I%20envied%20are%20tied%20to%20someone%20else's%20vision.%20They'll%20spend%20their%20lives%20working%20for%20a%20company%20and%20doing%20things%20they%20don't%20necessarily%20enjoy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20these%20people%20would%20never%20get%20the%20recognition%20they%20deserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20work%20might%20win%20someone%20else's%20wealth%20and%20fame%20while%20they%20stay%20in%20the%20background%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BExpendable%2C%20they%20will%20constantly%20worry%20about%20getting%20laid%20off%20and%20planning%20their%20lives%20around%20their%20salaries%2C%20budgeting%20to%20pay%20bills%20and%20likely%20renting%20a%20place%20to%20live%2C%26quot%3B%20predicted%20Ms%20Dar%2C%20who%20pursued%20a%20master's%20in%20computer%20science%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Dar%20shared%20that%20she%20had%20envisioned%20a%20different%20life%20for%20herself-%20one%20unbound%20by%20%26quot%3Bthe%20expectations%20of%20an%20academic%20institution%20or%20the%20constraints%20of%20a%20corporate%20office.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20opting%20out%20of%20a%20career%20in%20academia%20or%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%20she%20explained%20that%20she%20could%20focus%20on%20exploring%20and%20learning%20about%20topics%20that%20genuinely%20interested%20her%2C%20rather%20than%20being%20limited%20to%20subjects%20deemed%20important%20by%20funding%20agencies.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20made%20%241%20million%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20revealed%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20financial%20side%20of%20her%20decision.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20video%2C%20Ms%20Dar%20explained%20that%20she%20started%20creating%20content%20on%20OnlyFans%20as%20a%20side%20project%20while%20pursuing%20her%20PhD.%20Through%20this%20venture%2C%20she%20earned%20%241%20million%2C%20which%20she%20used%20to%20pay%20off%20her%20family's%20mortgage%20and%20buy%20herself%20a%20car.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThankfully%2C%20I%20avoided%20taking%20out%20any%20student%20loans.%20Now%2C%20I%20have%20an%20investment%20portfolio%20and%20am%20planning%20to%20buy%20my%20own%20house.%20These%20accomplishments%20are%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20tangible%20rewards%20of%20carving%20my%20own%20path%20and%20the%20freedom%20it%20has%20brought%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20concluded%20her%20video%20by%20highlighting%20that%20most%20professors%20in%20the%20U.S.%20earn%20around%20%24100%2C000%20annually%20and%20often%20spend%20more%20time%20writing%20grant%20proposals%20than%20conducting%20actual%20research-%20a%20lifestyle%20she%20felt%20wasn't%20aligned%20with%20her%20vision%20for%20herself.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734943680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fdmpnu5v_zara-dar_625x300_23_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmade-over-1-million-youtube-zara-dar-quits-phd-to-become-adult-content-creator-7313245%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMoving%20on%20to%20doing%20OnlyFans%20and%20content%20creation%20full-time%20it's%20not%20just%20a%20career%20choice%20it%20feels%20kind%20of%20like%20a%20gamble%20on%20the%20direction%20of%20my%20entire%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Dar%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmade-over-1-million-youtube-zara-dar-quits-phd-to-become-adult-content-creator-7313245%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chaudhry's%20Sparkl%20bags%20%244%20mn%20from%20Zomato%2C%20Zerodha%20founders%20and%20others%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734943596000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fchaudhry-s-sparkle-bags-4-mn-from-zomato-zerodha-founders-and-others-124122300462_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chaudhry%2C%20whose%20previous%20firm%20Aakash%20Educational%20Services%20(AESL)%20was%20bought%20by%20Byju's%20in%202021%2C%20has%20secured%20a%20seed%20investment%20of%20about%20%244%20million%20for%20his%20new%20edtech%20venture%20Sparkl%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fchaudhry-s-sparkle-bags-4-mn-from-zomato-zerodha-founders-and-others-124122300462_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20Ensured%20Ambedkar's%20Inclusion%20in%20Constituent%20Assembly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20days%20dedicated%20by%20Parliament%20to%20deliberate%20on%20the%2075th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20culminated%20in%20a%20heated%20debate%20over%20Dr.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20drafting%20committee%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly.%20Both%20sides%20of%20the%20aisle%20sought%20to%20claim%20the%20legacy%20of%20Ambedkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20by%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20which%20was%20intended%20to%20ridicule%20the%20Opposition's%20claim%20to%20represent%20Ambedkar's%20legacy%2C%20did%20not%20provoke%20a%20response%20in%20the%20House%20but%20led%20to%20an%20unprecedented%20uproar%20outside%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2012-second%20clip%20of%20the%20minister's%20speech%20was%20widely%20circulated%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20suggestions%20that%20he%20had%20been%20unfair%20to%20Ambedkar's%20memory.%20In%20fairness%2C%20it%20must%20be%20asked%20why%20the%20Opposition%20did%20not%20protest%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20as%20the%20minister%20spoke.%20Amit%20Shah%20maintains%20that%20his%20speech%20was%20clipped%20out%20of%20context%20to%20create%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%2C%20which%20seemed%20disorganised%20during%20the%20session%2C%20with%20allies%20distancing%20themselves%20from%20Congress%20slogans%2C%20suddenly%20found%20a%20cause%20to%20rally%20around.%20The%20shameful%20events%20on%20the%20penultimate%20day%20of%20the%20winter%20session%20may%20well%20be%20the%20darkest%20episode%20in%20our%20constitutional%20history.%20MPs%20are%20elected%20to%20debate%20issues%20in%20Parliament%2C%20not%20to%20spar%20like%20gladiators%20at%20its%20gates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Winter%20Session%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20worked%20for%20just%2057%25%20of%20the%20time%2C%20while%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20functioned%20for%20only%2043%25.%20Very%20little%20productive%20work%20is%20being%20done%20in%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20focusing%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20House%2C%20we%20now%20witness%20hyperactivity%20at%20the%20gates.%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20holds%20mock%20media%20interviews%2C%20and%20Opposition%20MPs%20climb%20the%20ramparts%20of%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building.%20Despite%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker's%20direction%20that%20no%20demonstrations%20be%20held%20at%20the%20gates%2C%20ruling%20party%20MPs%20block%20the%20entrances%20to%20counter%20the%20Opposition%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllegations%20of%20fisticuffs%20being%20exchanged%20and%20two%20MPs%20being%20injured%20have%20emerged.%20The%20Delhi%20Police's%20Crime%20Branch%20has%20been%20tasked%20with%20investigating%20the%20matter.%20Politicians'%20activities%20on%20Parliament%20premises%20are%20now%20subject%20to%20a%20criminal%20probe%E2%80%94an%20unprecedented%20situation%20in%20the%20annals%20of%20parliamentary%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20now%20come%20back%20to%20the%20Ambedkar%20legacy%20and%20who%20has%20claims%20over%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20was%20formed%20in%201946%2C%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20faced%20strong%20opposition%20to%20his%20candidacy%20from%20Congress%20stalwarts%2C%20including%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20he%20failed%20to%20get%20elected%20from%20his%20then%20home%20state%20of%20Bombay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20Congress%20leaders%20in%20Bombay%20were%20reportedly%20of%20the%20view%20that%20%E2%80%9Capart%20from%20the%20doors%2C%20the%20windows%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20were%20closed%20to%20Bhimrao%20Ambedkar.%E2%80%9D%20The%20reason%20for%20their%20opposition%20stemmed%20from%20Ambedkar's%20differences%20with%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20which%20led%20to%20his%201933%20fast%20in%20Yerwada%20Jail%20and%20the%20subsequent%20signing%20of%20the%20Poona%20Pact.%20In%201936%2C%20Ambedkar%20had%20also%20formed%20the%20Indian%20Labour%20Party%2C%20which%20contested%20elections%20against%20Congress%20in%20provincial%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Ambedkar%20formed%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20Federation%20(SCF)%2C%20which%20came%20to%20his%20aid%20in%201946%2C%20ensuring%20his%20election%20to%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20from%20the%20Jessore-Khulna%20constituency%20in%20undivided%20Bengal.%20Jogendra%20Nath%20Mandal%2C%20a%20Namosudra%20SCF%20legislator%2C%20helped%20secure%20Ambedkar's%20election%20through%20the%20Bengal%20Legislature.%20Ambedkar%20won%20with%20the%20highest%20votes%2C%20with%20Netaji%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose's%20brother%2C%20Sarat%20Chandra%20Bose%2C%20securing%20one%20vote%20fewer.%20Other%20prominent%20figures%2C%20including%20Shyama%20Prasad%20Mukherjee%20and%20Frank%20Anthony%2C%20were%20also%20elected%20alongside%20Ambedkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20partition%20of%201947%20saw%20Jessore-Khulna%20going%20to%20the%20East%20Bengal%20Province%20of%20the%20Dominion%20of%20Pakistan.%20The%20member%20elected%20from%20Jessore-Khulna%20was%20to%20be%20included%20in%20the%20Pakistan%20Constituent%20Assembly%20in%20Karachi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20his%20election%20in%201946%2C%20Ambedkar%20had%20made%20significant%20contributions%20to%20the%20proceedings%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20of%20undivided%20India.%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20thus%20sent%20a%20request%20to%20B.G.%20Kher%2C%20the%20then%20Premier%20(as%20Chief%20Ministers%20were%20called%20at%20the%20time)%20of%20Bombay%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20ensure%20Ambedkar's%20election%20to%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20anxious%20that%20he%20should%20attend%20the%20next%20session%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%2C%20commencing%20from%20the%2014th%20of%20July%201947%2C%20and%20it%20is%20therefore%20necessary%20that%20he%20should%20be%20elected%20immediately%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20wrote%20to%20Kher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKher%20set%20aside%20his%20opposition%2C%20which%20had%20previously%20forced%20Ambedkar%20to%20seek%20election%20from%20Bengal.%20He%20arranged%20for%20the%20member%20from%20Poona%20(Pune)%2C%20Mukund%20Ramrao%20Jayakar%2C%20to%20resign.%20The%20resulting%20by-election%20was%20won%20by%20Ambedkar%2C%20while%20Jayakar%20was%20appointed%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Bombay%20government.%3Cbr%3E%5CnAmbedkar's%20Bengal%20connection%20came%20to%20light%20during%20the%20Winter%20Session%20of%202015%20when%2C%20at%20the%20instance%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Constitution%20Day%20was%20first%20observed%20on%20November%2026.%20Trinamool%20Congress%20floor%20leader%20and%20veteran%20parliamentarian%20Sudip%20Bandopadhyay%20mentioned%20it%20in%20his%20tribute.%20A%20controversy%20followed%2C%20with%20BJP%20MP%20from%20West%20Bengal's%20Darjeeling%20seat%2C%20Surinder%20Ahluwalia%2C%20disputing%20the%20claim%20and%20asserting%20that%20Ambedkar%20was%20elected%20from%20Bombay%20State.%20Both%20MPs%20were%20right.%20%C2%A0Ambedkar%2C%20while%20presiding%20over%20the%20Drafting%20Committee%20(which%20had%2010%20members%2C%20with%20B.N.%20Rau%20writing%20the%20document)%2C%20was%20indeed%20a%20member%20from%20Bombay%20when%20the%20Constitution%20was%20adopted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbedkar's%20differences%20with%20Congress%2C%20which%20led%20to%20his%20resignation%20from%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru's%20cabinet%20in%201951%20and%20his%20subsequent%20unsuccessful%20bids%20to%20enter%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20Bombay%20North-Central%20(in%20the%20first%20general%20election%20of%201952)%20and%20from%20Bhandara%20(in%20a%201954%20by-election)%2C%20are%20often%20highlighted.%20It%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%2C%20despite%20contesting%20against%20Congress%20on%20both%20occasions%2C%20he%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%201952%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20Federation%20(SCF).%20This%20was%20made%20possible%20because%20the%20Congress%20did%20not%20oppose%20his%20Rajya%20Sabha%20nomination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20spotlight%20is%20on%20Ambedkar%2C%20it%20is%20worthwhile%20to%20recall%20the%20comment%20he%20made%20about%20his%20role%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Hindus%20wanted%20the%20Vedas%2C%20and%20they%20sent%20for%20(Ved)%20Vyasa%2C%20who%20was%20not%20a%20caste%20Hindu.%20The%20Hindus%20wanted%20the%20epic%20Ramayana%20and%20they%20sent%20for%20Valmiki%2C%20who%20was%20an%20untouchable.%20The%20Hindus%20want%20a%20constitution%2C%20and%20they%20have%20sent%20for%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20legacy%20of%20Bhimrao%20Ambedkar%20is%20being%20debated%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20recognise%20that%20not%20all%20in%20Congress%20were%20opposed%20to%20him.%20He%20had%20been%20both%20an%20opponent%20and%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20before%20the%20Constitution%20was%20formally%20adopted%20on%20November%2026%2C%201949%2C%20the%20Organiser%2C%20in%20its%20November%2023%2C%201949%20edition%2C%20carried%20an%20article%20by%20the%20then%20RSS%20Sarsanghchalak%20lamenting%20that%20%E2%80%9Cunique%20constitutional%20developments%20in%20ancient%20Bharat%E2%80%9D%20had%20been%20glossed%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbedkar's%20Constitution%20of%20India%20is%20a%20product%20of%20competing%20ideas%20that%20were%20incorporated%20into%20a%20historic%20text.%20The%20behaviour%20of%20current%20MPs%2C%20both%20inside%20the%20House%20and%20outside%2C%20stands%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20Ambedkarite%20thought%2C%20whose%20legacy%20everyone%20seems%20eager%20to%20usurp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734943500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-12%2Fbr-ambedkar_650x400_41512541559.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frajendra-prasad-ensured-ambedkars-inclusion-in-constituent-assembly-7313393%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20was%20formed%20in%201946%2C%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20faced%20strong%20opposition%20to%20his%20candidacy%20from%20Congress%20stalwarts%2C%20including%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frajendra-prasad-ensured-ambedkars-inclusion-in-constituent-assembly-7313393%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Japanese%20car%20g