0Reddy%20had%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERipples%20of%20change%3A%20Turning%20ideas%20into%20action%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20began%20the%20entangling%20and%20detangling%20of%20more%20threads.%20The%20students%20had%20the%20arduous%20task%20of%20connecting%20the%20dots%20between%20the%20water%20crisis%20and%20the%20floods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakshita%2C%20a%20student%2C%20observed%20a%20distinct%20connection%20between%20their%20school%20coursework%20and%20the%20questions%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20find%20answers%20to.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20special%20science%2C%20we%20learned%20about%20the%20types%20of%20rain.%20Our%20science%20curriculum%20helped%20us%20understand%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20layout%20and%20the%20materials%20it%20was%20built%20with.%20For%20measuring%20rain%2C%20we%20turned%20to%20maths.%20And%20to%20understand%20people%E2%80%99s%20perspectives%2C%20social%20science%20came%20to%20the%20rescue%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20her%20eyes%20gleaming%20as%20she%20draws%20the%20parallels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20of%20this%20%E2%80%9Cthinking%20out%20loud%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20students%20put%20it%2C%20was%20a%20detailed%20causal%20map%20that%20they%20made%20to%20summarise%20their%20interview%20outcomes.%20In%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20map%20was%20a%20question%20written%20in%20a%20sizable%20font%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20is%20it%20flooding%20so%20much%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201755px)%20100vw%2C%201755px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FTinker-Refuse-Reduce-Reuse-Recyle-Upcycle-and-Innovate-4_page-0001_11zon-1733754801.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221755%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20students%20made%20a%20causal%20map%20to%20understand%20%26quot%3BWhy%20is%20it%20flooding%20so%20much%3F%26quot%3B%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com